title: Easy Lamb Rump & Avocado Cos Salad with Dijon Honey Dressing & Mayonnaise
description: Dive into a guilt-free feast with our lamb rump cos salad! Wholesome goodness meets delectable delight as lamb rump,
roasted to perfection, takes centre stage amidst crisp cos lettuce, tomatoes and avocado. Top it off with a punch dijon honey
dressing for a taste explosion!

